entry.summary: 3a. 3.a.i. This program is meant to provide users a way to efficiently use their time and improve their productivity. 3.a.ii. In the video the user can input numbers and operation signs and the program would either output the answer to the expression or tell the user to try again with proper inputs. The program allows users to edit previous entries or delete them all. 3.a.iii. The input of the program is a string of the desired equation to be solved. The user can input letters and signs. It also takes input from the user through the many buttons on the screen. The output as seen in the video is the answer to the expression.
